      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 32-35.</p><p>Masterful Inspiration</p><p>Beginning at 23rd level, your Bardic Die becomes a d20. In addition, whenever you use your Bardic Inspiration, you can cast a spell of 5th level or lower with a casting time of one action or bonus action as part of the same bonus action.</p></div>",
